    "installTarget": "@components/aurora/artifact.tsx",
    "taxonomy": "ai"
  },
  "docs": "Aurora block that expects `aurora-tokens` to be installed first.\n\nDefault install target: `@components/aurora/artifact.tsx`.\n\nRegistry dependencies: `aurora-tokens`, `aurora-button`.",
