  "docs": "Aurora component that expects `aurora-tokens` to be installed first.\n\nDefault install target: `@ui/aurora/filter-bar.tsx`.\n\nRegistry dependencies: `aurora-tokens`, `aurora-button`, `aurora-input`, `aurora-select`.",
